description: Creates a signal catalog using your existing VSS formatted content from your local device.

parameters.name: name
parameters.description: The name of the signal catalog to import.

parameters.name: vss
parameters.description: The contents of the Vehicle Signal Specification (VSS) configuration. VSS is a precise language used to describe and model signals in vehicle networks. vssJson (string) --- Provides the VSS in JSON format.

nested_params.name: vssJson
nested_params.description: Provides the VSS in JSON format.

parameters.name: tags
parameters.description: Metadata that can be used to manage the signal catalog. (dict) --- A set of key/value pairs that are used to manage the resource. The tag's key. The tag's value.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the imported signal catalog.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the imported signal catalog.
